WorkItem.Description:
Agi gives quite a lot of dodge to paladins.
 
With kings, the 22agi enchant on cloak should give the same as 18.3 dodge rating, yet it is rated as worse than the 12dodge rating enchant for mitigation.
 
I think the crit and armour values are correct.
 
Agi should give 1% dodge per 48 agi for paladins (with kings) I think? Something like that anyway.
 
At the moment its hardly giving any dodge at all!
WorkItem.Summary: [ProtPaladin] Agility is being underrating for Dodge
